                        <head>Irene Polinskaya</head>

                        <div>
                            <p>The introduction, epigraphic editions, commentaries, and metadata descriptions in English and Russian 
                                are by Irene POLINSKAYA. Information on Find Contexts derives from inventory cards of the Berezan collection 
                                at the State Hermitage Museum.</p>
                            <p>The identification and dating of ceramics are by Sergey SOLOVYOV 
                                (Keeper of the Berezan Collection, The State Hermitage Museum).</p>
                            <p>The inscriptions were encoded following the
                                EpiDoc Guidelines for use of XML for ancient documentary editions.
                               The website and supporting materials are the work of Gabriel
                                BODARD, Irene POLINSKAYA and colleagues at the Department of Digital
                                Humanities and King’s Digital Lab, King's College London.</p>
                            
                            
